name: 1 LB Chicken Wings
description: Windsor's favorite wings, made fresh to order. Choose breaded, boneless, or naked. Hand tossed in over 25 sauces, these wings are always cooked to crispy perfection and coated just how you like 'em.

name: 2 LB Chicken Wings
description: Windsor's favorite wings, made fresh to order. 2 Free Flavors. Choose breaded, boneless, or naked. Hand-tossed in over 25 sauces.

name: Original Chicken
description: Crispy, juicy, and seasoned with our house spice blend. This chicken burger is hand breaded, fried to a golden crunch, and finished with lettuce, pickles, and mayo on a toasted Brioche bun.

name: H.M.B
description: Sweet heat meets savory spice. Golden fried chicken, layered with our signature spices, pickles, Jalapenos, Comeback Sauce, Honey Mustard Sauce and Coleslaw. Made fresh in Windsor, it's bold, tangy, and seriously addictive.

name: Nashville Burger
description: Fried crispy, spiced hot, and full of flavor. We coat our chicken in our signature Nashville seasoning, fry it fresh, and finish with comeback sauce, pickles and Lettuce. It's Windsor's top pick for that perfect balance of heat and crunch.

name: Crispy Chicken Wrap
description: Fast, fresh, and full of flavor. Crispy chicken with lettuce, tomato and your choice of spicy or mayo sauce, wrapped tight in a soft tortilla. A Windsor classic that's easy to grab, hard to forget.

name: 3 Chicken Tenders
description: Crispy outside. Juicy inside. Always made fresh. Our tenders are hand breaded and seasoned with our custom spice mix, then fried until golden. Served with your choice of dip.

name: 5 Chicken Tenders
description: Crispy outside. Juicy inside. Always made fresh. Our tenders are hand breaded and seasoned with our custom spice mix, then fried until golden. Served with your choice of 2 dips.

name: Hot Shots
description: Bold spice. Big crunch. Bite sized. Fresh chicken chunks tossed in our signature blend of spices, then flash fried until crispy.

name: Fries
description: Crispy, golden and clear coated. Choose regular or large. Our fries are cooked fresh and seasoned just right, great on their own or as the perfect sidekick.

name: Onion Rings
description: Choose regular or large. Our Onion rings are cooked fresh and seasoned just right.

name: Potato Wedges
description: Thick cut, crispy outside, fluffy inside. Seasoned with a light blend of spices, our wedges are hot, hearty, and seriously satisfying.

name: Poutine
description: Crispy fries, real cheese curds, rich savory gravy. Our Windsor style poutine starts with golden fries, loaded with fresh cheese curds and smothered in hot vegetarian gravy.

name: Fried Dill Pickles
description: Tangy, crunchy, and seriously snackable. Zesty pickle slices coated in a seasoned breading and fried until crispy.

name: Cheezy Tater Bombs (6)
description: Crispy golden potato bites stuffed with gooey cheddar cheese. Perfectly fried, melty on the inside, crunchy on the outside.

name: Jalapeno Poppers
description: Creamy, cheesy heat in every crispy bite. (7 Pieces) Our jalapeÃ±o poppers are stuffed with smooth cream cheese, lightly breaded, and fried until golden.

name: Funnel Cake Sticks
description: Crispy, sweet, and dusted in cinnamon sugar. These golden funnel cake sticks are deep fried to perfection and served with warm caramel dip.

name: MilkShake
description: Thick, creamy, and blended to order. Choose classic vanilla or rich chocolate. Our milkshakes are smooth, sweet, and pair perfectly with wings, burgers, or anything in between.
